reviews.headline: I would buy this product again and again
reviews.comments: Espectacular for my skin( very dry)

reviews.headline: Does not feel like makeup
reviews.comments:
I had a salesperson match my skin color and I am obsessed with this product. It goes on light, stays on all day and has a nice coverage that does not look like I have anything on.  I have had several compliments since I started using it.
Good pick and perfect sunscreen as well.

reviews.headline: I will buy this product again
reviews.comments: This is my new foundation.

reviews.headline: i would recommend
reviews.comments: I'm 58 years old and I have been using this specific product for several years now and I LOVE it. It is more for the light make up users but you still get that youthful glow look. It does not cake.

reviews.headline: Super smooth and great coverage
reviews.comments: People have said my skin looks brighter and the feel is amazing highly recommend

reviews.headline: Too much ORANGE glow
reviews.comments: I was not pleased with my results. I bought the fair light shade.  At first application, it appeared fine. Soon after, I noticed how the longer I left the product on my face the oranger the glow became.  I washed it off within 2 hours. I never even made it outside into the sun! New product bought at Ulta store. Not expired. Nope...never...ever...again. Shame. It had promising ingredients like 2% Niacinamide, Hyaluronic Acid, and green tea extract, too.

reviews.headline: This product did not work for me

The nude glow did not work for me. I need more coverage than this provides and will need to return.
Thx. Barb

reviews.headline: Patchy
reviews.comments: I orderd the wrong shade, but also a little bit patchy on my skin, maybe I should try with my right shade

reviews.headline: Love!
reviews.comments: I am so happy I decided to purchase the ic cosmetic cc skin tint. It leaves a dewy glow on my dry skin that I absolutely love. Highly recommended

reviews.headline: Best makeup for my "mature" skin !
reviews.comments:
This product is the best option for my skin. Very lightweight but you can build more coverage if you need to. Since I have mature skin it's very important to me that it doesn't cakey. "Less is more "  is absolutely true !
this product works so well for me that I highly recommend it.

reviews.headline: I was surprised
reviews.comments: This glided on my face like butter-blended so well and was light. I'm super picky about what I put on my face. I've used everything from Chanel, Ila, Lancome, etc, but right now, I'm really loving this random sale purchase I made. I'd buy it even when it's not on sale.

reviews.headline: Light coverage but glowing skin
reviews.comments: This is my fave of the it cosmetics cc creams. The only drawback is it is very light coverage, but doesn't settle into pores or fine lines. I still need a concealer to cover redness.

reviews.headline: Very good
reviews.comments: My face gets pretty red and I've tried many foundations to help tone it down. This foundation and Nars is great. The formula is very light and doesn't leave my skin oily. I've gotten a lot of compliments wearing it.

reviews.headline: Light and blends well
reviews.comments: This is nice lightweight foundation for summer. It blends well and feels nice and light on the skin. I do think I will switch to a more medium coverage foundation in fall.

reviews.comments: Feels good on the skin very smooth and smells good

faceoff_positive.comments:
I have been on the hunt for a good foundation for a couple years, ever since the formula in my last foundation changed. I'm only 33 and was sick and tired of these foundations settling into my pores and forehead lines. I felt like most foundations were aging me 10 years and highlighting my flaws. Not this stuff!

This Foundation gives me an awesome glow, goes on so smooth (I use a sponge) and doesn't cake up. I have yellow undertones so I purchased the Light (W). It was a little darker than what I expected for a Light, but I'm going to order another in the Fair for winter.
faceoff_positive.headline: FINALLY FOUND THE PERFECT FOUNDATION

faceoff_negative.comments: I ordered Light Fair like I always do in my illumination CC and the Oil-free bye bye foundation - but it came MUCH darker  and I can't even use it - it's a totally different color!!
faceoff_negative.headline: Right color - but why is it wrong?
